				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				As to the making of Bows...<BR>
You need the staff ( elm to start with )After something like lvl 83 go with Ashwood.. <BR>
2nd item is the string <BR>
Cams Dont do it unless you are something like 110 Or better..<BR>
As to the Plain and whittling Blade,, <BR>
Both must be in a inventroy MAIN slot (1 in each)<BR>
The plain will allow you to create Recurve, and the whittling Knife take what would be a Rough Bow into A Real bow,, ( I think )<BR>
<BR>
I think it took me about 10 hours and 40pp to go from lvl 5 up to 101,,, <BR>
<BR>
Aenelen 29 Paladin<BR>
Xegony
				</font>
